  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7115199/" class="title-link">社会资本</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7115199"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/meteors/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2058664-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/meteors/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">水月孤桥</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-09-30"
      class="main-meta">2014-09-30 13:50:08</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7115199_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  “社会资本”是社会学中常见的一个概念，强调的是一种社会关系。早期主要是由Coleman和Bourdieu等社会学家进行研究。Coleman在《社会理论的基础》之中对于“social capital&#34;有深入的介绍。近些年来，一些经济学家也慢慢地对这个领域产生兴趣，并展开研究。     在Tirole的《公...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7115199_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7115199_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
